APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2010-1911. Young v. State.

Hamilton App. No. C-090771. Discretionary appeal accepted on Proposition of Law Nos. I, II, III, and IV; cause held for the decision in 2009-0088, State v. Williams, Warren App. No. CA2008-02-029, 2008-Ohio-6195; and briefing schedule stayed.

Pfeifer and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., would also accept the appeal on Proposition of Law Nos. V and VI without holding.
